            <t:abstract>
                <t:p>Sǝbḥata fǝqur-hymn to St George of Lydda.
                  The manuscript tradition seems to differ in varying degrees from the printed edition.
                In some of the modern editions of <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1961Mashaf">Maṣḥafa saʿātāt</t:ref>,
              it is one of a few sǝbḥata fǝqur-hymns dedicated to various saints.</t:p>
            </t:abstract>
